data.description: This Single-Family 4-bedroom 3-bath Village Lakes Community Home has all the essentials.  The Cathedral Ceilings and vinyl Wood Floors invite you into your living and dining space. Your bright kitchen is central and comes with all appliances.  The kitchen sink has a direct backyard view, and the breakfast bar overlooks the cozy Family Room with gas or wood burning Fireplace. Exit to the lush backyard from your new dual-paned glass sliding door to pick your Mandarin, Apple, Lemon, & Avocado Trees.  Your Private Backyard retreat is a well-groomed enclosed space.  The attached 2-Car Garage allows private and secure entry into your home directly from the car.  Upstairs you will find your sleeping quarters with Master suite boasting his and her closets.  The roof was replaced just 2 years ago, new dual-paned windows were installed along the backside of the home, and hardwood floor was installed in the living areas, hallways, stairs, & new bedroom carpet.  Trash is included with property tax!  The Community provides a scenic Greenbelt Walking Trail to the Pool/Spa, and 2 Lakes with Pond & Wildlife like ducks, geese, cranes, and turtles.  Guest parking is available.  Pride of ownership!
